
@PostMapping - /addProductToCart

In POSTMAN - 

Set to POST - http://localhost:9090/cartController/addProductToCart

Put in Body - 

{
    "email" : "kunalshetty1070@gmail.com",
    "price" : 390,
    "productName" : "Chicken Tandoori Pizza L"
}

----------------------------------------------------------------------

@GetMapping - viewAllCart/{email}

In POSTMAN - 

Set to GET - http://localhost:9090/cartController/viewAllCart/kunalshetty1070@gmail.com

------------------------------------------------------------------------

@DeleteMapping - removeProduct/{cartId}

In POSTMAN - 

Set to DELETE - http://localhost:9090/cartController/removeProduct/1